OL,3,CLittle-Pengelly dismisses 'panto
OL,4,Cseason' criticism over multi-year
OL,5,Cbudget
OL,7,FThe Deputy First Minister has
OL,8,Fdismissed criticism that 'panto season
OL,9,Fhas begun' over budget tensions at the
OL,10,FExecutive table.
OL,12,FEmma Little-Pengelly was answering a
OL,13,Fquestion from the Leader of the
OL,14,FOpposition at Stormont, the SDLP's
OL,15,FMatthew O'Toole.
