OL,3,CLittle-Pengelly dismisses 'panto
OL,4,Cseason' criticism over multi-year
OL,5,Cbudget
OL,7,F"Deputy First Minister, can you
OL,8,Fguarantee that there will be a multi-
OL,9,Fyear budget and that your party will
OL,10,Fnot block one? "
OL,12,FMs Little-Pengelly said she was 'fully
OL,13,Fsupportive' of a multi-year budget:
OL,14,F"We have a challenge at the moment
OL,15,Fwithin our big departments. That is no
OL,16,Flaughing matter. It is not a joke. It
OL,17,Fis a serious matter and we will be
OL,18,Fengaging in that in the next number of
OL,19,Fdays, in the next number of weeks,
OL,20,Fbecause I am fully supportive of a
OL,21,Fmulti-year budget.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/5
