OL,3,CLittle-Pengelly dismisses 'panto
OL,4,Cseason' criticism over multi-year
OL,5,Cbudget
OL,7,F"There are challenges within that,
OL,8,Fparticularly looking across all of the
OL,9,Fneeds and the demands within each of
OL,10,Fthose departments, but I am giving an
OL,11,Fabsolute commitment to work with
OL,12,Feveryone to try to drive forward the
OL,13,Foutcomes that we want to see."
OL,15,FLast month, the Finance Minister
OL,16,Fconfirmed plans to introduce the first
OL,17,Fmulti-year budget Stormont has seen in
OL,18,Frecent years.
